Classes in info.jonclark.treegraft.core.tokens used by info.jonclark.treegraft.chartparser
Token
          Abstracts Terminal tokens away from Strings so that we can use more efficient representations such as integers for storing them in memory and doing comparisons while still retaining the ability to use Strings for ease of debugging.
TokenFactory
          Responsible for mapping input strings to unique tokens so that they can be efficiently compared and hashed.
